<Author>NathalieMH
<Content>Unfriendly staff, small and noisy rooms Unfriendly staff, small and noisy rooms. The first room we got was at the back of the hotel. There was no noice from the street but we could hear the people in de next room breathing. We got another room but this room was even worse. A little bigger, but a lot more noisy (from the street as well as from our neighbours in rooms next to ours and above and under ours)! We stayed here for six nights (it was very busy in Barcelona and we could not find another hotel) and every night there were lots of shouting and drunk people in the hallway. Cleaning started early with loud sounds in the hallway from early in the morning untill the end of the afternoon (so no siesta for us). The restaurant of this hotel was closed, this was not mentioned on the website. 
