<Content>Good value and central location Overall I would recommend this hotel. The positives:* Good location - only a couple of minutes walk to Plaza Catalunya, La Rambla, and also to the Museum of Contemporary Art* Very clean room with both a bath and shower (you'll be glad of a soak in the bath after walking all day around the city!)* Lovely roof terrace with views over the city and a hot tub* Free internet access * Staff were very helpful and will store luggage until it is time to check in* Free bottled water at receptionThe negatives:* The rooms are quite small* The hotel can be rather noisy at night due to British hen / stag party guests slamming doors and shouting when they stagger back from the bars / clubs.* I had a room with a window that opened onto an internal atrium so no fresh air which I was disappointed about as I prefer fresh air to a/c. 
